# Frontend -> Backend API origin for auth/session calls.
# Leave EMPTY (default) to use the built-in Next.js proxy at /api/* -> FastAPI.
# This is required for SameSite=lax session cookies to work (avoids cross-origin cookie blocking).
# Set to a full URL only for remote/staging backends (e.g. https://api.example.com).
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_ORIGIN=
